             General Motors Co. plans to
announce tomorrow that it will invest more than $850 million to
upgrade five North American factories, three people familiar
with the matter said.  
 The spending will preserve 1,600 jobs, said the people, who
asked not to be identified because the details arenâ€™t public
yet.  
